<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<BES xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="BES.xsd">
	<Analysis>
		<Title>ServerMon: URL Check Results</Title>
		<Description><![CDATA[
<p>Reads back the URL check results reported by the
<a href="https://github.com/jgstew/bigfix-proxyagent-servermon">bigfix-proxyagent-servermon</a>
Management Extender plugin.</p>
<p>Only relevant on proxied devices reported by the servermon plugin: the first
relevance clause is false on ordinary BES clients (and short-circuits, so the
plugin-specific inspectors are never evaluated there), and the second clause
only evaluates true where the inspectors from
<code>Inspectors/servermon.inspectors</code> are defined.</p>
<p><code>HTTP Response Code</code> is <code>0</code> when no HTTP response was
received at all (DNS, TCP, TLS, or timeout failure); see
<code>HTTP Check Result</code> for the reason.</p>
<p><code>HTTP Check Last Error</code> / <code>HTTP Check Last Error Time</code>
record the most recent failed check. The plugin remembers each device's last
error in a local state file and re-sends it with every report, so transient
errors stay visible after they clear, until the next error replaces them.
These properties read "no error recorded" for a device that has never failed.</p>
<h2>SSL Certificate Expirations:</h2><BR><BR>
<?relevance html concatenation of tables of (it whose(it as string as trimmed string != "") | tr of td of "None in the next 20 days") of html concatenations of trs of tds of ("SSL Certificate for " & item 1 of it & (if item 0 of it < 0 then " expired" else " expires") & " in " & (item 0 of it as string) & " days!") of ((it / day) of (it as time - now) whose(it < 20 * day) of values of it, names of computers of it) of results of bes properties "SSL Certificate Expires" ?>
]]></Description>
		<Relevance>in proxy agent context</Relevance>
		<Relevance>exists servermon version</Relevance>
		<Source>bigfix-proxyagent-servermon</Source>
		<SourceReleaseDate>2026-07-16</SourceReleaseDate>
		<MIMEField>
			<Name>x-fixlet-modification-time</Name>
			<Value>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 18:30:00 +0000</Value>
		</MIMEField>
		<Domain>BESC</Domain>
		<Property Name="URL" ID="1" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[url of http check]]></Property>
		<Property Name="HTTP Response Code" ID="2" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[response code of http check]]></Property>
		<Property Name="HTTP Check Result" ID="3" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[result of http check]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Check Success" ID="4" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[success of http check]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Match Found" ID="5" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists match found of http check then (match found of http check) as string else "no match configured"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Response Time (ms)" ID="6" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[response time ms of http check]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Last Check Time" ID="7" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[last check time]]></Property>
		<Property Name="ServerMon Version" ID="9" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[servermon version]]></Property>
		<Property Name="HTTP Check Last Error" ID="10" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists last error of http check then last error of http check else "no error recorded"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="HTTP Check Last Error Time" ID="11" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists last error time of http check then (last error time of http check) as string else "no error recorded"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Bad String Found" ID="14" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists bad string found of http check then (bad string found of http check) as string else "no no_match configured"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Last URL Contact Time" ID="15" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists last device report time then (last device report time) as string else "never responded"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Refresh Interval (Minutes)" ID="16" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists refresh interval then (refresh interval) as string else "n/a"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="TLS Version" ID="12" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists tls version of http check then tls version of http check else "n/a"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="SSL Certificate Expires" ID="17" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[ssl certificate expirations of http checks]]></Property>
		<Property Name="SSL Certificate Days Remaining" ID="18" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists ssl certificate expiration of http check then (((ssl certificate expiration of http check) - now) / day) as integer as string else "n/a"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Remote IP Address" ID="13" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists remote ip address of http check then remote ip address of http check else "n/a"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Connect Time (ms)" ID="20" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists connect time ms of http check then (connect time ms of http check) as string else "n/a"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Network Hops" ID="21" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists network hops of http check then (network hops of http check) as string else "n/a"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Proxy Agent Plugin" ID="19" EvaluationPeriod="PT30M"><![CDATA[if exists proxy agent plugin then ((name of it & " v" & (version of it as string) & " on " & host of it & " @ " & (last report time of it as string)) of proxy agent plugin) else "n/a"]]></Property>
	</Analysis>
</BES>
